name: Fists Tee
description: A Professionally screen-printed garment, Printed on 100% Ringspun cotton and finalised with custom inside-nape-printed labels. 100% Cotton pre-shrunk ringspun jersey, 5/8” Rib knit collar, tubular knit, seamless twin needle collar. Twin needle sleeves and bottom hem. Taped neck and shoulders. ¼ turned to eliminate centre crease. Size Chest Small - 34/36" Medium - 38/40" Large - 42/44" Recommended to wash; - Inside out - At 30 degrees Celsius - Don't iron the design
